    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/d9c9f9bfd81f63ac543f56d8c92f4925.poster.avif?t=1721557813\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/d9c9f9bfd81f63ac543f56d8c92f4925.webm?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/d9c9f9bfd81f63ac543f56d8c92f4925.mp4?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >描述</h2>你所看到的一切都笼罩着神秘的迷雾。而你自己也仿佛溶于其中。你是谁？在哪里？为什么？这些问题都还没有答案。<br>因为这里<strong>它</strong>是......闪闪发光，然后消逝。消失了。但它以钢铁般的决心充斥着你的身体。<br>黑暗世界的所有敌意引出了另一个问题--它难道不曾希望你醒来吗？所有的答案，在你面前。在只有一丝光亮的地方。那就是<strong>它</strong>引导你的地方。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/bb57fc1528f4c25980e7712aac33840a.poster.avif?t=1721557813\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/bb57fc1528f4c25980e7712aac33840a.webm?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/bb57fc1528f4c25980e7712aac33840a.mp4?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还有更多</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>让自己沉浸在一个黑暗、神秘的世界中。<br></li><li>寻找最意想不到的解决方案，继续你的冒险。<br></li><li>揭开这个世界和你自己的秘密。<br></li><li>突破这个邪恶的地方的每一个角落。<br></li><li>挑战不同的独特敌人和情况。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/746aff876ff10dcb803fa98759857e08.poster.avif?t=1721557813\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/746aff876ff10dcb803fa98759857e08.webm?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/746aff876ff10dcb803fa98759857e08.mp4?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一头栽进一个黑暗的世界，那里的每一声沙沙声都是另一个危险的信号。除了空虚和毁灭，你能在其中找到什么吗？看看你是否能找到自己，或者你是否会在未知的沟渠中继续成为一个破裂的瓷器面具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/e265ee2b586694befbd31d424f1d5e55.poster.avif?t=1721557813\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/e265ee2b586694befbd31d424f1d5e55.webm?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/e265ee2b586694befbd31d424f1d5e55.mp4?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/f2ce4c7e969eee46fae4da839d81c0de.poster.avif?t=1721557813\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/f2ce4c7e969eee46fae4da839d81c0de.webm?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808440/extras/f2ce4c7e969eee46fae4da839d81c0de.mp4?t=1721557813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
